<% provide(:title, "Strength") %>
<h1>GcBaseball#strength</h1>
<p>Here we have the list of all Strength drills we may perscribe. If you click on each drill, you will be able to see a short description of each drill. One great resource for learning proper technique while lifting is 
Alan Thrall on Youtube. Check out their YouTube channel for more information, and helpful video to get you started.</p>
<div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
    <% @strength.each_with_index do |drill, index| %>
      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h4 class="panel-title">
            <a id="heading<%= index+1 %>" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse<%= index+1 %>" >
              <%= drill.name %> 
            </a>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse<%= index+1 %>" data-parent="#heading<%= index+1 %>" class="panel-collapse collapse">
          <div class="panel-body">
            <%= drill.description %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</p>
